Package com.rubynaxela.kyanite.util

Class JSONDictonary

java.lang.Object
com.rubynaxela.kyanite.util.JSONDictonary
All Implemented Interfaces:
Dictionary, Map<String,Object>
Direct Known Subclasses:
DataAsset
public class JSONDictonary extends Object implements Dictionary
Map-like class designed to hold JSON data. Provides methods for reading and writing the values as values of specific Java types.
